Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.11,0:00:20.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kai...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.39,0:00:30.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't believe that you were \NReversed... but it's true, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.89,0:00:31.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.91,0:00:36.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's the kind of look \NI wanna see on your face, Aichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.91,0:00:37.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:45.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna test you to see if you're \Nreally good enough to fight Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.05,0:01:00.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just Kai... I have to \Nget Miwa back to normal, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.68,0:01:03.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore... I have to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:06.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:08.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to fight Miwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:09.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:11.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.60,0:01:13.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.69,0:01:23.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi, your fight is with Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.69,0:01:25.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:28.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight, Miwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.92,0:01:33.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Tokura, but I'm not interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:37.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you afraid of losing to me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:40.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! You know how to hurt a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:44.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Tokura. A fight it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:43.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida... By showing Aichi your fighting \Nform, you got him back on track.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:51.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you brought the Reversed Kamui back \Nto normal with a desperate fight, Aichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:53.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:57.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:10.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the last time. \NYou representing Miyaji...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:12.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you responsible for Hitsue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:18.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the only thing that's different is that\Nnow the fate of the world is on the line?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:26.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:37.33,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Form of Friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:40.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lizard Soldier, Conroe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle Maiden, Amenohoakari!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:47.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A new first Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:52.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean she's powered up even \Nmore from her previous Genesis deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:54.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:58.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ride Dragon Monk, Gojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:05.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Conroe moves back. And it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:07.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.52,0:05:10.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ride Witch of Cats, Cumin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:12.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:15.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:22.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ride Dragon Knight, Nehalem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:24.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Call!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:27.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:36.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ride Battle Maiden, Sahohime!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:39.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cider moves back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:44.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I call Goddess of Trees, Jupiter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.98,0:05:53.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,3 to 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:56.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They were tied up to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:57.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:04.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa... Your offhanded consideration...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:10.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You watched the store for me, \Nknowing I wanted to practice fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:14.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.07,0:06:19.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was troubled over \Nbeing on a losing streak...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:28.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No good... I can't win like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.69,0:06:32.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't drag Aichi and the others down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:34.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:37.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:42.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:47.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kai went off somewhere. I'm waiting \Nand waiting, but he's a no-show.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:51.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me kill some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:54.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'm really not fit to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:55.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:57.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, right now is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:07:01.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, fear is often worse \Nthan the danger itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:04.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too much discretion \Nbecomes stupidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:08.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think too much, \NI get a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.23,0:07:12.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At a time like that, I try \Nto do some physical activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:13.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:19.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:25.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured more things out through actual \Nfighting than just thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:34.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:37.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. We gotta stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:38.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:43.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:48.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line. Thanks \Nfor hanging out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:57.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can always offhandedly pick \Nup on what somebody is feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:03.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Indomitable emperor dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:06.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,with the unwavering fighting spirit \Nthat resides in your fangs,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:08.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,turn despair into light!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:13.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ride Dauntless Drive Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:20.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Call! Berserk Dragon! Counterblast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:22.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're retired, Jupiter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:26.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I call Seal Dragon, Kersey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:29.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Conroe's Counterblast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:31.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Conroe goes to the Drop Zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:35.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I add this guy to my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:39.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Barri... A perfect guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:45.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect guard...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't all bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:51.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that she knows he's got one, \Nshe can come up with a strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:55.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're actually smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:56.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to say "actually"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always offhanded about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:08.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But just once, I've seen you serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:11.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was during the local preliminaries...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:16.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, you act like you're not \Nreally interested, but the truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:19.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you're passionate when \Nit comes to your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:24.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that fight, I saw how serious \Nyou could be for their sakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:29.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're different now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:33.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:37.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kai chose Link Joker, \Nand now you guys are enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:42.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to become Kai's ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:46.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm helping him do what he wants to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:48.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what are friends are for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:52.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As I suspected, you don't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:55.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take you down, Miwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:58.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! That's a scary look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:00.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I stand and draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:05.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With the heavenly power \Nthat resides within you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:10.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,seek out intelligence, courage, and justice, \Nthen connect them with the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:15.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ride Regalia of Wisdom, Angelica!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:21.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Call!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:24.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grappa attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:26.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:30.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Angelica! Soulcharge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:37.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, I Soulcharge \Nwith Amenohoakari!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:41.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:44.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Drive trigger check.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:47.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heal trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:52.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I give the power to Ordain, \Nand heal 1 damage point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:56.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:01.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Healing damage is a big deal here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:04.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's 4 to 2 now! She can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:06.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so, Brother Aichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:08.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:12.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think you can beat me playing \Nat this level, you're sorely mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.53,0:11:16.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have a trump card.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:19.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand and draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:25.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cursed power! Fangs thirsting for madness!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:28.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mete out despair deeper than any other!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:30.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Break ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:35.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dauntless Dominate Dragon "Reverse"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:11:59.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The break ride gives it +10000 power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:01.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it gains a skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:07.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I call Calamity Tower Wyvern!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:08.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Soulblast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:09.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:13.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And now the real game begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:18.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruler of darkness, return everything \Nto nothingness with your accursed roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:22.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dauntless "Reverse's" Limit Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:25.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I Lock Calamity Tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:29.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, it gains a skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.92,0:12:33.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Two skills?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:35.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:38.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dauntless "Reverse" attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:44.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Drive trigger check!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:48.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Limit Break activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:51.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can retire one of your \Ngrade 1 or lower rear-guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:53.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Amenohoakari!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:59.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dauntless "Reverse" gets +3000 power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.37,0:13:02.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That ain't no ordinary retiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:06.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He just decreased the number of \NSoulcharges she can do next turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:06.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.38,0:13:13.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the power of Miwa's Reverse deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:16.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Second check.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:19.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Critical trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:22.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I give all of the effects \Nto Dauntless "Reverse"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:29.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damage trigger check.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:38.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, break ride skill activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:43.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By putting three cards from my hand into \Nthe Drop Zone, Dauntless "Reverse" stands!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:50.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my trump card...\N Death Spiral Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:56.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The spiral of death doesn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:59.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dauntless "Reverse" attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:07.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:13.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Five elements created \Nby the almighty goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:16.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your soul acts as a catalyst \Nfor ultimate change!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:18.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Descend in all your radiance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:22.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shield Goddess, Aegis!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.15,0:14:30.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quintet Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:34.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quintet Wall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:38.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guarding alone, the total is 25000...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:39.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:42.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:45.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...I guard with a shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:50.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I give the skill to my Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:54.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot. But whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:56.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Drive trigger check.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:14:59.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Limit Break activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:01.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cider, get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.72,0:15:04.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Second check!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:09.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Critical trigger! I give \Nall the effects to Berserk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:13.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cider's skill activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:17.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I move a unit from the \Nguardian circle to the Drop Zone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:19.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to move it again to the Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:25.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Soul increased to \Nseven cards all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:28.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She charged up her Soul with a \Nlot of cards while defending!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:32.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That Quintet Wall combo is formidable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:45.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Berserk attacks with a boost \Nfrom Seal Dragon, Kersey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:48.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard! And intercept!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.73,0:15:54.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rats. Then I've got no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:57.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dominate Drive attacks Ordain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.98,0:16:01.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When it attacks, it gains +3000 power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:03.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:08.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:11.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She protected herself against that attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:13.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:14.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:18.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Final Turn, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:25.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings for your friend haven't \Nchanged. That's what you said, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:26.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:28.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.87,0:16:34.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you are now, you're just following \Nyour friend, because you're Reversed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.36,0:16:38.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't do it because you wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:41.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it to try to keep him from \Ngoing in the wrong direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:45.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what a true friend does, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:51.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before being Reversed, you acted \Nas Kai's beneficial brakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.25,0:16:56.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the person I'm going to bring back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:17:02.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all... I'm your friend, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:06.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand and draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:13.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Goddess who appears in response to \Nthe call of the regalia of wisdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:16.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your sword of intelligence and foresight
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:19.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,to cut through the tangled skein of fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:21.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Break ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:26.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Omniscience Regalia, Minerva!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:33.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I use three cards for the Soulblast,\N and draw two cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:37.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, it gets +10000 power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:43.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ordain moves. I call Jupiter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:47.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch the miracle of a goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:49.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ordain's skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:55.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I take one unit with "Regalia" in the name from my \NDrop Zone, and move it to the bottom of my deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:58.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Minerva gets +5000 power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:00.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Angelica!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:05.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And one more unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:10.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A combo with fellow Regalia units!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:13.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.33,0:18:15.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast! Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:17.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Intercept!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:19.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Drive trigger check.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:24.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! The attack doesn't go through!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:29.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After I'm done attacking, Minerva's \Ntrue worth comes into play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:30.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:33.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Intelligence is stronger than the sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:40.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,God of intelligence, gather here! Guide me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:42.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Limit Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:46.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva, stand! +5000 power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:52.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:59.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get in \NKai's way! Perfect guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.73,0:19:01.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Drive trigger check!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:05.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Critical trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:09.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I give both the power and the \Nextra critical to Jupiter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:11.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So a perfect guard here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:15.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Misaki took that into account.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:16.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:21.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jupiter attacks with a boost from Ordain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:26.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.44,0:19:31.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I lose, Kai will...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:36.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...be alone again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:40.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gamble everything on a trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:44.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damage trigger... check!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:47.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Second check...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:54.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:08.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:12.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She did it! Boss Lady won!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.49,0:20:13.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:15.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:19.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She made the most of Genesis's \Nspecial characteristics.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:21.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a deck that she obviously \Nput a lot of thought into.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.52,0:20:29.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not only Naoki. When I wasn't paying \Nattention, Misaki was preparing for this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:33.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:36.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not alone. We're here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:39.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:41.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:46.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:51.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.33,0:20:53.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:58.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamui and... the guys from Miyaji...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:05.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:08.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I've left you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:15.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:16.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:18.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can walk on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:23.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this... discouragement?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:26.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It just means you thought a little \Ntoo much about your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:27.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:31.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thought too much... about my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:34.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an embarrassing expression \Nif I've ever heard one...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.11,0:21:38.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So even while Reversed, \Nyou thought about your friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.60,0:21:40.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's a man for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:43.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A man who's honorable and loyal! {made this up, since he talks about the kanji for "man"}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:48.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, guys, I don't remember anything, \Nbut don't try to snow job me with cheap praise!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.99,0:22:00.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me, Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.85,0:23:59.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa... You know, you're really...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.10,0:24:01.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Save your breath. I know the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.96,0:24:02.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.86,0:24:05.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it right before I was Reversed...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.12,0:24:07.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That I had to be there for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.09,0:24:08.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.13,0:24:10.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kai... Is it because of Ren and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.95,0:24:12.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that even possible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.47,0:24:15.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kai, you were my goal and Ren's rival...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.25,0:24:18.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Two Leaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.90,0:24:25.69,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,The Two Leaders
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.58,0:24:21.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm going to do everything \Nin my power to stop Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.59,0:24:23.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my duty!